author: Cleo Abram
description:
You can find the asteroid belt between Mars and Jupiter. It’s a massive span of space cluttered with huge jagged rocks leftover from when our solar system formed and it’s captured our imaginations. 

Most movies depict it as a super crowded and dangerous section of the solar system, but how realistic is that? 

NASA has sent 9 spacecraft through successfully. Could you?

Subscribe for more optimistic science and tech stories!

title: Could You Fly Through the Asteroid Belt?
